        "Admission process",
        "Admission information"
      ],
      "responses": [
        "You can apply online through the university admission portal.",
        "Admission requires SSC and HSC certificates."
      ]
    },

    {
      "tag": "programming",
      "patterns": [
        "What is Python?",
        "Explain programming",
        "What is AI?"
      ],
      "responses": [
        "Python is a popular programming language.",
        "Artificial Intelligence enables machines to simulate human intelligence."
      ]
    },

    {
      "tag": "thanks",
      "patterns": ["Thanks", "Thank you", "Nice"],
      "responses": [
        "You are welcome!",
        "Happy to help!"
      ]
    }
